1
00:00:00,515 --> 00:00:03,617
My dearest, darling Anna.
我亲爱的安娜宝贝儿

2
00:00:10,053 --> 00:00:13,617
I'm writing this on a Sunday night in London.
我在一个星期日的晚上 在伦敦写下了这封信

3
00:00:16,471 --> 00:00:18,720
If you're reading this,
当你读到这封信时

4
00:00:18,808 --> 00:00:21,075
then you barely knew me
也许你会对我感到陌生

5
00:00:21,173 --> 00:00:24,355
and may have no memory of who I am.
也许根本想不起来我是谁

6
00:00:25,840 --> 00:00:27,564
I am your mother.
我是你的妈妈

7
00:00:29,377 --> 00:00:33,102
You were born in an air raid in the middle of a war
你出生在战争时期的一次空袭中

8
00:00:33,262 --> 00:00:36,311
to two people who loved each other.
是爸爸妈妈的爱情结晶

9
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:44,622
Our year together in the house in Hampstead has been the happiest time of my life.
我们在汉普斯特的这栋房子里  度过的一年是我一生中最幸福的时光

10
00:00:51,555 --> 00:00:54,408
Today you took your first steps.
今天 你学会了走路

11
00:00:58,186 --> 00:01:03,582
I am so grateful  that I saw you walk  for the first time with your father by my side.
我很感激有你爸爸陪在我身边

